data.description: This home just oozes character and charm. Well maintained mid-century rancher with hardwood floors throughout. Sited on a mature lot in the heart of Manheim Township this home provides an enclosed front porch and screened rear porch. Gas heat, hot water, and fireplace. Newer windows and doors as well as newer roof. Oversized 1 car garage with an additional attached storage space. Home is move in ready!  UPDATE 1/30:  WE HAVE RECEIVED AN OFFER AND ARE SETTING AN OFFER DEADLINE OF 8 PM ON WEDNESDAY, JANUARY 31.
